  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Vibe coding doesn't scale. It always ends in two thousand line files and agents hallucinating patterns.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6b1ba56e2f307cf946b172de55e4332e3284d2b933fc507652c4000e84f37d56",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 5.061958333333333,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Here's the fix. I ran a ninety minute workshop on this.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6b5655aef4e1a2566b8f1f89f0a8eca25ea6080ce99788ff53f1e053f1c3e484",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399583333333335,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 16
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Six strategies, no fluff. They turn any messy codebase into something an agent can actually navigate.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b80cd8731ca927f8c6811fb4ce58471220746fe3bd013d53ca30e9f64e58d416",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 4.82975,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 27
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Ninety seven engineers in the room. Real codebases.",
      "checksum": "sha256:976437c39f1b793cc76eb96f1b1801751c4e648362c3125785d38285f3309e1f",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 2.6470833333333332,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 43
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "And one specific failure mode is killing most of them.",
      "checksum": "sha256:38ecdc4fa82ee5bbe91bae4d1d18ca1b8560998ee635855051cd3e876213a173",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 2.600625,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 51
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "File size isn't the metric. A two thousand line file with three imports is fine.",
      "checksum": "sha256:10ef0d9a5c0322697a645323e113a8ff54d8137000590e5fd879319c4c2e6041",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 4.272458333333334,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 61
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Coupling is what kills you. Six strategies.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c4767452d939035b8a0257fc1ef1bab29a9d94fb3e892c654b77c5fccd0afa4f",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 2.1826666666666665,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 76
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "One \u2014 vertical slices. Organize by feature, not by layer.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d8fb8d8de58390e4f9d885c1a0b2961bb0edfe4539393c879e3cfb82d6266ff0",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650416666666667,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 83
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Two \u2014 brownfield day one. Use sub-agents to derive your A I layer.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4e05c5db6452652e480136ac10aa7b3ca26b1d139311afb63808bde26d41fdb6",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043333333333335,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 93
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Three \u2014 three tier context. Global, on demand, and ticket only.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5f3eb25cf6068983e796301a005e811236134c580e26d0c1d8045299f69c9946",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 3.2507916666666667,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 106
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Four \u2014 focused prime commands. One per slice.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e892596a2323b587fce94f4d459dfe6c54d60c4130395acdd4e69ceaad6bd9ea",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 2.50775,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 117
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Five \u2014 parallel worktrees. Multiple agents, zero collisions.",
      "checksum": "sha256:573c7127c183fb76474eb4dd8eb3f002845d4f9efefd274765296d1055a7cca4",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650416666666667,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 125
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Six \u2014 size by coupling, not by line count.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0a64e527bc2cdd9ba810b819ffd73351938ea969a0d81f69efe84b02ae71b17a",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 2.414875,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 133
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "The most precious resource isn't your wallet.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0b3751aff61cc4047dc453d08d84a10e8a886bee41c656eacb0b4b8068d2b547",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 2.275541666666667,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 142
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "It's the context. Protect it like a finite tank.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d88f2e564e601b02d5647478461a3436b64c047756800d585312a90a8523553c",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 2.5542083333333334,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 149
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "So \u2014 vertical slices, or shared test folders.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0013fc4afbee34bf03656893b30ef0324ce146b6fd011125353d7b6245dcb0a3",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 2.50775,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 158
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Which one are you running? Drop your take.",
      "checksum": "sha256:bd83eac862a5d0e99e3032d907d517f888e718558ca4939e2ce0fd57abecc0b4",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 2.1826666666666665,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 166
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "And if you want to learn more about AI, check out the dynamous dot AI community.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d01d802f811b1fc829c7edcfab600abdc85092a91ad7b50fb667392cbe5b394b",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 4.086708333333333,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 174
    }
  ]
